        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/10424563-narrative-of-sojourner-truth">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4161638-denise-ballentine?shelf=nonfiction">nonfiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4161638-denise-ballentine?shelf=biography-memoir">biography-memoir</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4161638-denise-ballentine?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
