        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer264951743" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13567568968968174767">This is an important piece of historical literature by Sojourner Truth to primarily point out the evils of slavery. It is helpful to read a biography of her first and be familiar with her life. This little volume was penned for her by someone else, as she could not read nor write. This narrative was published for her to sell as a way to help support herself as she traveled about speaking against slavery. This only covers the beginning of her life, and she had many more adventures that followed t</span>
  <span id="freeText13567568968968174767" style="display:none">This is an important piece of historical literature by Sojourner Truth to primarily point out the evils of slavery. It is helpful to read a biography of her first and be familiar with her life. This little volume was penned for her by someone else, as she could not read nor write. This narrative was published for her to sell as a way to help support herself as she traveled about speaking against slavery. This only covers the beginning of her life, and she had many more adventures that followed this account. The woman writing this for her does insert some of her own interpretations, ideas, and examples, so this is not precisely in her own words. Worth being aware of. </span>
  <a data-text-id="13567568968968174767" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


