    <a title="Claire Baxter" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19065005-claire-baxter"><img alt="Claire Baxter" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1365042145p2/19065005.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
