          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1491549891" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8103310238463061492">This narrative isn&apos;t the most thrilling read. In part that is because of the style of the time, and it is because Truth is holding back. But it is worth reading simply to get to know the famous woman a bit more. The best passages are those about family, in particular, her relationship with her son.</span>
  <span id="freeText8103310238463061492" style="display:none">This narrative isn't the most thrilling read. In part that is because of the style of the time, and it is because Truth is holding back. But it is worth reading simply to get to know the famous woman a bit more. The best passages are those about family, in particular, her relationship with her son.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8103310238463061492" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
